title: Keds President Commitment to Empower Women
itunes:title: Keds President Commitment to Empower Women
description:
Gillian Meek, President at Keds, talks about the Keds Hand-Book for Women and the movement of women empowerment. She says more of women's stories need to be told.

Hosts: Carol Massar and Jason Kelly. Producer: Doni Holloway.
